<span class="displaytext">arlington, va -- today, u.s. senator mel martinez issued the following statement on (candidate full)'s new spanish ad: <p>"this election is about more than beautiful words, it's about who decides how your money is spent, who chooses your doctor, and our standing around the world. (candidate full) is a tested leader who loves america, puts his country first, and trusts you to make the best decisions for your family. at this time of great uncertainty, hispanics and all americans can trust in the leadership and experience of (candidate full). he, like i, has lived the american dream and wants to bring prosperity and security to all our families."</p></span>



